#define FNAME_SET   1
#define FNAME_NOTSET   2

Detailed Description

The following three defines specify to the tree_find_module function how it should deal with the presence/absence of the filename attribute of the module structure.

Define Documentation

#define FNAME_DONTCARE   3
 

Specifies that the tree_find_module function should not care about the value of filename.

#define FNAME_NOTSET   2
 

Specifies that the tree_find_module function should only match if filename is not set.

#define FNAME_SET   1
 

9 Specifies that the tree_find_module function should only match if filename is set.
